Summer in a Glass: How to Make Delicious Watermelon Lemonade in No Time

🍉🍋 Watermelon Lemonade 🍋🍉

Ingredients:
4 cups cut seedless watermelon (approx ⅓ - ½ whole watermelon)
¾ cup lemon juice (approx. 4 lemons)
½ cup lime juice (approx. 4 limes)
½ cup sugar
4 cups water
Watermelon vodka (optional)
Mint leaves for garnish

Directions:
1️⃣ In a blender or food processor, purée the watermelon into a smooth liquid. Strain the mixture. 
2️⃣ In a separate bowl juice the lemons and limes. Strain the mixture. 
3️⃣ In a large pitcher combine the water and sugar. Stir until sugar is dissolved. 
4️⃣ Add the strained watermelon purée and the strained lemon-lime juice. 
5️⃣ Stir well and taste. If you want it a little sweeter, add an additional ¼ cup of sugar. It it’s too sweet for you, add ½ cup more water. 
6️⃣ When serving, add 1 - 2 ozs of watermelon vodka for added kick. 
7️⃣ Garnish with mint leaves and enjoy!
.
.
.

Hey there, my fellow food enthusiasts and flavor fanatics! I’ve got something incredibly exciting to share with you all today. It’s a little gem called Jam Vino, and trust me, it’s about to rock your taste buds like never before! 🍷🍇

So, picture this: the sweet, juicy flavors of fruit, combined with the smooth richness of wine. Can you imagine anything more tempting and indulgent? Well, that’s exactly what Jam Vino brings to the table, my friends. It’s like a culinary love story, where the fruit and the wine come together in perfect harmony. 🎶🍓🍷

As lots of you know, I grew up in sunny Northern California, not too far from wine country. Combined with my Alabama roots, I’ve got a unique perspective on blending flavors that’ll knock your socks off. 

Jam Vino isn’t your average jam. It’s an experience, and each jar is crafted with love, care, and a sprinkle of my culinary genius. ✨👩🏽‍🍳. There are three signature flavors: 
🍷Blackberry Merlot
🍷Raspberry Moscato 
🍷Strueberry Blanc (strawberries & blueberries in Sauvignon Blanc)

Imagine spreading Jam Vino on your morning toast, or on a charcuterie board. Oh, and let’s not forget about the incredible desserts you can create with it! (think cheesecake for starters!) Seriously, this stuff will make your taste buds do a happy dance. 🍞🧀🍰

Every spoonful is like a party in your mouth, and trust me, everyone’s invited! 🎊🎉. Available now at JamVino.com…you gotta try it! Use the code WELCOME20 for 20% off. 

To learn more and see more about Jam Vino type “Jam Vino” in the comments and I’ll send you a DM with info.  Cheers 🥂✨ #JamVino #WineInfusedJam #ChefLorious
